Licey al Medio

Licey al Medio is a city in Santiago Province, in Dominican Republic.

GPS Coordinates of Licey al Medio, Santiago Province, Dominican Republic

Licey al Medio is located on the latitude of 19.45 and longitude of -70.6 and has a geohash of d7my9ky8kyb3.

Cities and Towns near Licey al Medio

The nearest significant population center from Licey al Medio is San Víctor Arriba in Espaillat Province, Dominican Republic, located 7 kilometers or 4 miles ↗ NE of the city. Other locations in close proximity include Juan López Abajo (Espaillat Province, Dominican Republic) located 10 km (6 mi) → E and Moca (Espaillat Province, Dominican Republic) located 11 km (7 mi) ↗ NE of Licey al Medio.
